(THUNDER RUMBLING)

01:04.378 --> 01:06.903
BUG: Now I lay me
down to sleep,

01:06.980 --> 01:08.607
I pray the Lord
my soul to keep.

01:09.249 --> 01:11.479
If I should die
before I wake,

01:11.818 --> 01:14.218
I pray the Lord
my soul to take.

01:14.287 --> 01:16.380
NEWSCASTER:
Before tonight's murder,
there has been no clue

01:16.456 --> 01:18.117
as to who
this killer might be.

01:18.225 --> 01:20.853
But now the Riverton Ripper
and the knife he uses

01:20.927 --> 01:23.657
have been caught
by a high-definition
security camera.

01:23.730 --> 01:24.992
SARAH: Any day, now.
NEWSCASTER: Police say

01:25.065 --> 01:28.296
that the killer
is a Caucasian male
in his mid-to-late 30s.

01:28.368 --> 01:29.926
It's too dark to see his face

01:30.003 --> 01:33.166
but the quality
of the image has allowed
forensic technicians

01:33.240 --> 01:34.639
to zoom in and
enhance it enough

01:34.708 --> 01:36.335
to make out
the word ''Vengeance''

01:36.410 --> 01:39.106
etched on the blade
of the Ripper's weapon.

01:39.179 --> 01:40.771
No one was in the
area at the time...

01:40.847 --> 01:42.405
SARAH: That's beautiful, Abel.

01:42.716 --> 01:44.877
And Leah's going
to love that house.

01:45.051 --> 01:46.712
Shameless distraction device.

01:47.087 --> 01:48.111
Come to bed.

01:48.188 --> 01:50.019
The news is too scary
for me to watch alone.

01:50.090 --> 01:51.216
Okay, Sarah,
I'll be up soon.

01:51.291 --> 01:54.454
NEWSCASTER: We consulted
local psychiatrist
Dr. William Blake.

01:54.761 --> 01:55.955
Oh, shit!

01:56.196 --> 01:58.323
(GROANING)
NEWSCASTER:
Here's what he had to say.

01:58.398 --> 02:00.161
DR. BLAKE:
The identity of
a killer of this sort

02:00.233 --> 02:02.758
may well not even
be known to himself.

02:02.836 --> 02:04.633
He could be
anywhere and anyone

02:04.704 --> 02:07.036
leading a normal life,
so far as he knows,

02:07.274 --> 02:08.798
and never dream
for an instant that,

02:08.875 --> 02:11.673
every so often,
he turns into a monster.

02:12.279 --> 02:13.337
ABEL: What is this?

02:13.413 --> 02:14.778
NEWSCASTER:
Twenty-one-year-old
Penny Anderson,

02:15.048 --> 02:16.174
a graduate student
at Boston University...

02:16.249 --> 02:17.511
WOMAN: (SCREAMING)
Somebody!

02:17.584 --> 02:19.211
NEWSCASTER:
...studying for a Ph.D.
in psychology.

02:19.286 --> 02:20.685
WOMAN: Help me!

02:21.388 --> 02:23.447
No!

02:23.890 --> 02:24.948
(GASPING)

02:25.025 --> 02:27.016
NEWSCASTER:
The victim's funeral
will be held tomorrow at...

02:27.093 --> 02:28.754
Dear God, tell me
this is a dream.

02:33.700 --> 02:34.997
ABEL (AS JAMES):
What's with the knife, Abel?

02:35.068 --> 02:36.729
What's with the blood?
It's really crazy stuff.

02:36.870 --> 02:40.237
It's not my knife, James!
I don't know what's with it.

02:40.440 --> 02:41.805
(AS PENNY)
I think someone
has broken in.

02:41.875 --> 02:43.502
(AS BRAD)
No one has broken in.
Come on, Penny.

02:43.577 --> 02:45.135
FEMALE VOICE: Please, Abel.
Blake said it could happen.

02:45.212 --> 02:47.407
A one in a million
chance, he said.

02:47.481 --> 02:48.880
(AS PENNY)
What if it did?

02:48.949 --> 02:51.144
He said to call him, 24/7.

02:51.218 --> 02:53.379
(AS BRAD) Abel, listen.
Call him now. You've
got to call Dr. Blake.

02:53.453 --> 02:56.081
(AS PENNY)
Please put down the knife.
Call the doctor.

02:56.156 --> 02:57.180
FEMALE VOICE:
God will help you.

02:59.392 --> 03:01.883
(AS RIPPER)
Call Dr. Blake,
and I kill your family.

03:01.995 --> 03:03.792
(GASPING)

03:03.864 --> 03:06.662
Sorry, sorry,
I just need a hug.

03:06.900 --> 03:09.391
That knife is so scary,
you know?

03:09.903 --> 03:10.927
What knife?

03:11.004 --> 03:13.598
SARAH: The Ripper's.
They've got it on tape.

03:14.274 --> 03:16.606
RIPPER:
Don't do something
stupid, Abel.

03:16.743 --> 03:17.732
Here's the deal.

03:17.811 --> 03:21.269
Just look the other way
when I kill and
your family stays alive.

03:22.682 --> 03:26.379
Turn me in,
and you'll live alone
in a house of blood.

03:27.087 --> 03:28.145
(GASPS)

03:28.221 --> 03:29.779
(PHONE RINGING)

03:32.492 --> 03:33.618
Hello?

03:33.693 --> 03:35.558
Abel, this is Dr. Blake.
ls everything okay?

03:35.629 --> 03:38.120
No, no, no.
Everything is not okay.
I found something.

03:38.965 --> 03:40.330
What did you find?

03:40.500 --> 03:41.626
A knife.

03:41.701 --> 03:45.137
Under my bench.
And not just any knife.

03:45.205 --> 03:47.105
The one on TV.
The Ripper's knife.

03:47.173 --> 03:49.334
I swear before God,
Dr. Blake, I didn't know.

03:49.409 --> 03:51.172
But the second
that I went to call you
there was somebody,

03:51.278 --> 03:53.872
and he said
don't call you, or else...

03:53.947 --> 03:55.915
DR. BLAKE: Or else?

03:55.982 --> 03:57.279
What?

03:57.350 --> 04:00.911
Or else he would
kill Sarah. And Leah.

04:00.987 --> 04:02.113
And the others, too.

04:02.188 --> 04:05.419
Abel, I'll be there
in 10 minutes.
I want you to tell Sarah

04:05.692 --> 04:08.320
to take Leah,
and drive to her sister's.

04:08.395 --> 04:10.659
I haven't told her
about this part of my life.

04:10.730 --> 04:12.220
But you swore
to me you would.

04:12.299 --> 04:13.288
That's part
of the agreement.

04:13.366 --> 04:14.924
Just get here
before it's too late!

04:15.001 --> 04:19.130
DR. BLAKE: Abel, have Sarah
drive to May's house,
with Leah.

04:19.238 --> 04:21.536
May is working nights
and Sarah is sound asleep.

04:21.608 --> 04:22.905
I can't just wake her up.

04:22.976 --> 04:24.500
DR. BLAKE: You have to!

04:24.578 --> 04:26.443
Abel?

04:26.513 --> 04:28.208
You there?

04:28.281 --> 04:29.873
Abel?

04:35.789 --> 04:38.087
(SCREAMING)

04:39.659 --> 04:41.490
ABEL: No! No!

04:47.267 --> 04:49.394
DR. BLAKE: What the hell
are you looking at?
Break the door down.

04:49.469 --> 04:50.766
ABEL: I won't let
you do this! I won't!

04:50.837 --> 04:52.031
DR. BLAKE:
Open the door. Abel!

04:52.105 --> 04:53.197
ABEL: I won't...

04:53.573 --> 04:55.040
DR. BLAKE: Abel!

04:56.343 --> 04:57.503
PATERSON: Police, open up!

04:57.577 --> 04:58.942
BOBBY: Mr. Plenkov, open up.

04:59.012 --> 05:00.274
DR. BLAKE: Abel,
open the door!

05:00.347 --> 05:01.939
BOBBY: Plenkov! Open up!

05:02.015 --> 05:03.414
PATERSON: Kick it in, Bobby.

05:04.184 --> 05:05.344
(DOOR CRASHING OPEN)

05:05.418 --> 05:07.409
DR. BLAKE: Get up
those stairs now!

05:07.854 --> 05:09.947
PATERSON: Which room?
On the right?

05:10.924 --> 05:12.619
Mr. Plenkov! Mr. Plenkov!

