Check him!

05:18.565 --> 05:19.862
Hey, sweetie.
Hey, sweetie, come here.

05:19.933 --> 05:21.161
Come here.
What's your name?

05:21.234 --> 05:22.496
BOBBY: No pulse, Frank.
What's your name, huh?

05:22.602 --> 05:24.433
BOBBY: I'll check the woman.
No, no, no, no,
look at me.

05:24.504 --> 05:26.665
You're okay, all right?
You're okay.

05:26.740 --> 05:29.265
Get away from me.

05:31.144 --> 05:32.577
Bobby.
Yeah?

05:32.646 --> 05:33.874
Get her downstairs.

05:33.947 --> 05:36.142
BOBBY:
Hey, sweetheart,
here we go.

05:37.717 --> 05:40.345
I got you.
You're going to be fine.

05:40.420 --> 05:42.047
PATERSON: Get in here.
Cover us.

05:42.122 --> 05:43.316
PATERSON: He's dead.

05:43.390 --> 05:45.051
So is Elvis.
You never know.

05:45.392 --> 05:46.416
You have an epi?

05:46.493 --> 05:47.858
We got it.

05:48.194 --> 05:50.594
JEANNE:
The mother is dead, too.
Way dead.

05:50.930 --> 05:53.524
You missed the kid,
you fuck.

05:53.600 --> 05:55.329
(AS RIPPER)
I'll get them all next time.

05:56.102 --> 05:57.694
Son of a bitch!

05:59.639 --> 06:01.470
GUS: Epinephrine kicks ass!

06:01.541 --> 06:03.270
