06:07.347 --> 06:10.316
Abel, I'll get you
to a hospital. Abel?

06:10.684 --> 06:12.345
You piece of shit.

06:12.852 --> 06:13.944
He's not a monster.

06:14.988 --> 06:16.182
What do you
call him, then?

06:16.289 --> 06:18.018
I call him mentally ill.

06:19.359 --> 06:21.418
(AS ABEL) Thank you
for stopping me.

06:22.128 --> 06:23.220
Abel.

06:23.496 --> 06:25.123
Forgive me.

06:25.765 --> 06:27.096
He's talking to you.

06:27.600 --> 06:28.999
Please!

06:29.602 --> 06:31.536
Would it hurt you
to be human?

06:31.771 --> 06:33.136
Just once?

06:35.842 --> 06:37.673
We'll let
God sort it out.

06:37.744 --> 06:39.109
Thank you.

06:42.248 --> 06:43.442
(SCREAMING)

06:43.516 --> 06:44.778
No, Abel!

06:44.851 --> 06:46.751
Abel, talk to me.

06:46.820 --> 06:48.412
(AS RIPPER)
Abel's not here.

06:52.292 --> 06:54.123
This is for you, you cunt!

06:54.194 --> 06:55.786
(GUNSHOT)

06:56.830 --> 06:58.161
That's for shut the fuck up.

07:07.207 --> 07:08.299
How's Mrs. King doing?

07:08.374 --> 07:09.534
Baby is two months premature.

07:09.609 --> 07:11.304
Dr. Carrie says
he's blind, too.

07:11.377 --> 07:13.277
Seven births in one hour,
all premature.

07:13.346 --> 07:14.608
What's going on here?
Anarchy!

07:15.348 --> 07:16.337
MAY: What else you got?

07:16.416 --> 07:19.351
We got a cop, Frank Paterson,
who took two in the vest.

07:19.419 --> 07:21.216
And?
And we got a perp.

07:21.287 --> 07:22.754
Go on.
Mid-30s,

07:22.822 --> 07:26.223
white male,
under constraint
and critical.

07:26.292 --> 07:29.921
Took multiple gunshots
and stab wounds.
EEG flat.

07:29.996 --> 07:32.726
Oh, and are you
ready for this?
We think he's the Ripper.

07:32.799 --> 07:34.232
What?
Family guy.

07:34.300 --> 07:35.665
Killed the wife,
tried to kill his kid.

07:36.035 --> 07:37.059
You got a name?

07:37.337 --> 07:39.237
Plenkov. Abel Plenkov.

07:41.841 --> 07:43.035
GUS: May, you copy?

07:44.210 --> 07:45.370
May?

07:45.912 --> 07:48.073
He said he'd get
them all next time.

07:48.148 --> 07:49.809
What do you think
he meant?

07:50.049 --> 07:52.142
Maybe he was talking
about his other
personalities.

07:53.019 --> 07:54.748
My family is from Haiti.

07:54.821 --> 07:56.083
And down there they don't say

07:56.156 --> 07:58.624
that someone like him
has multiple personalities.

07:58.691 --> 08:00.124
What do they say he has?

08:00.693 --> 08:02.217
Multiple souls.

08:02.729 --> 08:03.821
What's the difference?

08:04.264 --> 08:07.097
Personalities die
when the patient dies.

08:07.167 --> 08:08.259
Souls live on.

08:10.603 --> 08:13.299
It's all just superstition,
I suppose.

08:16.242 --> 08:17.869
Could you hand me
my jacket, please?

08:18.211 --> 08:20.304
It's cold as hell in here.

08:22.949 --> 08:23.973
Thanks.

08:25.285 --> 08:27.378
ls this your evidence bag?

08:27.720 --> 08:29.244
(SCREAMING)

08:30.824 --> 08:33.121
Get that fucker
under control!

08:35.028 --> 08:37.019
(RIPPER LAUGHING MANIACALLY)

08:37.263 --> 08:38.251
(SCREAMING)

08:43.970 --> 08:45.403
Shit!

08:50.610 --> 08:51.702
Frank!

08:51.778 --> 08:53.177
I can't believe
you fucking guys!

08:53.246 --> 08:54.611
You're supposed
to be watching him!

08:54.681 --> 08:56.308
You all right?
You good?
Fuck you!

08:56.382 --> 08:58.213
You're all right.
GUS: Let me see.
Get out of my way.

08:58.284 --> 08:59.911
Where the hell is Plenkov?
GUS: Let me see!

09:00.320 --> 09:01.480
PATERSON: Shit. Fix that!

09:05.792 --> 09:08.124
PATERSON: Call for backup!
I got Plenkov!

09:14.968 --> 09:16.162
PATERSON: Fuck!

09:30.783 --> 09:35.618
CROWD: One, two,
three, four, five,

09:35.688 --> 09:40.785
six, seven, eight,
nine, ten,

09:40.860 --> 09:43.294
11,12!

09:45.832 --> 09:48.266
BRANDON: The lights out!

09:48.334 --> 09:49.858
(ALARM RINGING)
(GASPING)

09:49.936 --> 09:51.528
BRANDON: Midnight!

09:51.838 --> 09:53.533
All right! This is it!

09:53.606 --> 09:55.335
Let the day begin!

09:55.408 --> 09:58.070
(ALL CHEERING)

10:03.883 --> 10:04.975
As you all know,

10:05.218 --> 10:07.209
Ripper Day
marks two things.

10:07.287 --> 10:09.482
One of them bad,
one of them good.

10:09.555 --> 10:13.787
The good part is,
it's the birthday
of seven of us here

10:13.860 --> 10:16.590
born 16 years ago tonight.

10:17.730 --> 10:18.856
Jerome King.

10:18.932 --> 10:20.456
Hey, Jerome.
(ALL WHOOPlNG)

10:21.034 --> 10:22.626
Alex Dunkelman.

10:24.137 --> 10:26.503
Jay Chan, with a new
Ripper puppet tonight.

10:27.206 --> 10:28.366
Bug Hellerman...

10:30.076 --> 10:31.134
Hellerman?

10:31.377 --> 10:33.004
ALEX: It's about time!

10:33.079 --> 10:35.411
BRANDON:
Better late than never,
I suppose.

10:35.481 --> 10:37.608
Where you been?
Sleeping.

10:37.684 --> 10:39.413
It's okay, Bug
takes a little longer

10:39.485 --> 10:41.077
because he's a little
slower, I guess.

10:41.154 --> 10:42.178
(ALL LAUGHING)

10:42.255 --> 10:45.053
Moving on to
Penelope Bryte over there,
by the ambulance,

10:45.124 --> 10:48.685
who, incidentally, knows God.
They speak daily.

10:48.761 --> 10:52.458
And to the beautiful
and gorgeous
Brittany Cunningham.

10:53.433 --> 10:55.526
And last, but,
of course, not least...

10:55.802 --> 10:57.269
ALL: Brandon O'Neil!

10:57.337 --> 10:58.565
Yes, sir!

10:58.638 --> 11:00.003
(ALL CHEERING)

11:00.073 --> 11:02.906
Thank you, thank you,
thank you very much.
Pleasure.

11:03.309 --> 11:06.506
Now, it's time for
the bad part, people.

11:06.980 --> 11:08.948
We of the Riverton Seven

11:09.015 --> 11:12.576
have had to share our birthday
with a monster,

11:13.086 --> 11:15.350
the serial killer
Abel Plenkov,

11:15.421 --> 11:17.548
who died at midnight
the day we were born.

11:18.725 --> 11:20.750
It's the Ripper.
CROWD: Ooh.

11:20.827 --> 11:23.523
Legend has it that we,
the Riverton Seven,

11:23.596 --> 11:26.622
are the mirrors
of Abel Plenkov's
personalities.

11:26.699 --> 11:28.530
The ones that
turned the Ripper in.

11:28.601 --> 11:30.933
And that the Ripper
still wants revenge.

11:31.004 --> 11:32.972
So Abel Plenkov is dead,

11:34.140 --> 11:35.767
but his ghost isn't.

11:36.075 --> 11:40.034
No, it lurks underneath
the old railroad bridge.
You've seen it.

11:40.613 --> 11:42.171
It sleeps in the river.

11:42.248 --> 11:44.546
It roams the darkest
corners of the woods

11:44.784 --> 11:48.083
just waiting for
the next Ripper Day
to come around.

11:48.421 --> 11:51.948
Because, on that day,
our birthday, tonight,

11:52.358 --> 11:54.918
the devil has told him
that he can take his revenge.

11:54.994 --> 11:58.430
But he can only
come out of the river
at this spot.

11:59.298 --> 12:02.324
And every year,
since we have been able,

12:02.402 --> 12:05.769
one of us Riverton Seven
has volunteered

12:05.972 --> 12:07.997
to drive him back
into the river

12:08.374 --> 12:09.739
where he belongs.

12:09.809 --> 12:12.175
And tonight is no exception.

12:12.578 --> 12:16.207
And I, personally,
have chosen to volunteer...

12:16.282 --> 12:17.613
GIRL 1 : Brandon?
GIRL 2: No!

12:17.683 --> 12:19.310
...to volunteer
Bug Hellerman, that is.

12:19.385 --> 12:20.443
(ALL CHEERING)

12:20.520 --> 12:21.782
BRANDON: It's your turn, Bug.

12:21.854 --> 12:23.913
All the rest of us
have done it.

12:23.990 --> 12:26.857
We will now summon the Ripper
from the river.

12:27.126 --> 12:32.291
If he appears yet again,
then Bug must slay him,
or we'll all die.

12:32.365 --> 12:33.855
Can you do it, Bug?
Save us!

12:33.933 --> 12:35.298
Let's call him up!

12:36.936 --> 12:39.268
If you can
hear me, Ripper,

12:39.739 --> 12:41.263
make yourself known!

12:41.607 --> 12:43.472
ALL: Make yourself known!

