12:57.423 --> 12:58.822
JEROME: What did I do?
ALEX: Bug is freaking out.

12:58.891 --> 13:00.654
BRANDON: Fear ye the Ripper!

13:00.726 --> 13:02.455
ALL: Fear ye the Ripper!

