What is that?

13:05.131 --> 13:06.291
JEROME: It's coming
from the woods.

13:07.100 --> 13:09.000
BRANDON: Whoa! Nice, Jay.
JAY: Damn right.

13:09.068 --> 13:12.526
Come on, Bug,
it's just a puppet.
Knock it over.

13:12.872 --> 13:13.930
ALL: Fear ye the Ripper!

13:14.006 --> 13:15.234
JEROME: Come on,
you can take him, Bug!

13:16.242 --> 13:17.903
Get in there, you pussy!

13:18.010 --> 13:19.875
Look at how scared he is!

13:19.946 --> 13:22.039
ALEX: Push him over.
BRANDON: Down
on your knees, Bug!

13:22.115 --> 13:23.605
JEROME: Slay
that beastie, Bug.

13:23.683 --> 13:25.173
BRANDON: Damn,
that is a big mother.

13:25.251 --> 13:26.513
JEROME: Bug, come on!

13:26.586 --> 13:28.281
BRANDON: Get him!
What are you doing?

13:28.354 --> 13:29.378
I can't do this!

13:29.455 --> 13:30.649
BRANDON:
But you must,
or we'll die!

13:30.723 --> 13:33.248
ALEX: Come on, Bug.
Just knock him down!
That's all you have to do.

