28:44.002 --> 28:46.436
No man does.
That's why you
got to fake it.

28:46.505 --> 28:48.097
Fake being a man
to be a man?

28:48.173 --> 28:50.073
That's the way it works.
So, you can't run.

28:50.142 --> 28:52.269
You have to face
your fear like a man.

28:52.344 --> 28:53.368
