were faking it good.

29:24.709 --> 29:25.937
I was?

29:26.011 --> 29:27.069
Abso-fucking-lutely.

29:27.879 --> 29:30.313
You now have
permission to shave.

29:30.715 --> 29:32.012
MR. KAISER:
As you know, class,

29:32.317 --> 29:34.376
we're nearing
the end of our reports
on living creatures.

29:35.387 --> 29:38.481
Dogs, fish, honeybees.

29:39.291 --> 29:43.250
