and Alex Dunkelman.

30:11.089 --> 30:12.351
Dumbfuckelman.

30:12.424 --> 30:14.016
Brandon.

30:14.092 --> 30:17.550
Our subject today
is about a bird.

30:19.297 --> 30:22.095
