30:27.005 --> 30:31.101
Our subject today
is the largest bird
in North America.

30:31.176 --> 30:33.770
Unchanged since
the Pleistocene Epoch

30:33.845 --> 30:36.575
and only recently
rescued from extinction.

30:36.648 --> 30:38.775
