30:38.984 --> 30:41.919
Gymnogyps californianus.

30:41.987 --> 30:43.249
Anus.

30:43.321 --> 30:44.811
MR. KAISER:
Brandon, second warning.

30:44.956 --> 30:46.617
The California Condor.

30:46.691 --> 30:47.953
(ALL GASPING)

30:48.026 --> 30:49.084
