somebody in there?

35:16.928 --> 35:18.327
No, no.
I got that covered.

35:18.396 --> 35:19.454
(GlRLS SHRIEKING)

35:19.531 --> 35:21.328
I'm sorry. Sorry, sorry.
Wrong bathroom, Jerome!

35:21.499 --> 35:23.660
