35:59.037 --> 36:00.766
(FAKES EVlL LAUGHTER)

36:03.341 --> 36:06.970
Brittany, window,
Chandelle, door,
Maria, you've got five.

36:16.254 --> 36:17.312
Go.

36:17.388 --> 36:20.152
The sophomores have paid
another year's protection
for their bikes.

36:20.225 --> 36:23.319
