week's organic chemistry
test are selling briskly.

36:24.529 --> 36:25.621
Bottom line,
$2,000 in the bank.

36:26.397 --> 36:28.228
We got her. (CHUCKLlNG)

36:28.299 --> 36:29.459
Good numbers.

36:29.634 --> 36:31.431
